@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pobaex(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(tmp) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.24) * (v0 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.70)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.49) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.01)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.61 - tmp + 0.64) / (v0 + 0.86 - v1 + 0.72)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.cos((tmp / (v2 + 0.99 + v2 + 0.41)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.11)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
